column3: {{c1::F}} - enter {{c2::hint}} mode; open in a background tab.
{{c1::h}} - {{c2::search}} for a domain name or URL.
{{c1::gi}} - go to last-used {{c2::input}} on the page.
{{c1::c-v}} - {{c2::send}} a single keystroke to the current website, bypassing bindings.
{{c1::c-o}} - {{c2::run}} a single normal mode binding when in ignore mode.
{{c1:::help hint}} - see all the other useful {{c2::hint}} modes.
{{c1:::help}} <keybinding> - to learn more about what a specific {{c2::key}} binding does.
{{c1::gF}} - {{c2::repeatedly}} open links until you press Escape.
{{c1::gu}} - go to the {{c2::parent}} of the current URL.
{{c1::gU}} - go to the {{c2::root}} domain of the current URL.
{{c1::c-b}} - jump to the {{c2::previous}} part of the page.
{{c1::a}} - {{c2::bookmark}} the current page and allow the URL to be modified.
{{c1::M}}<key> - bind a {{c2::quickmark}} to the given key.
{{c1::go}}<key> - open a given quickmark in {{c2::current tab}}.
{{c1::gn}}<key> - open a given quickmark in {{c2::new tab}}.
{{c1::gw}}<key> - open a given quickmark in {{c2::new window}}.
{{c1::O}} - {{c2::open}} a pre-load current URL in this tab.
{{c1::j}} - open a URL in a {{c2::new tab}}.
{{c1::J}} - open a pre-load current URL in a {{c2::new tab}}.
{{c1::w}} - open a URL in a {{c2::new window}}.
{{c1::W}} - open a pre-load current URL in a {{c2::new window}}.
{{c1::p}} - {{c2::paste}} the clipboard contents in the current tab.
{{c1::ga}} - go to the tab currently playing {{c2::audio}}.
{{c1::l}} - show a {{c2::list}} of open tabs in the current window.
{{c1::;p}} - {{c2::copy}} an element's text to the clipboard.
{{c1::;P}} - {{c2::copy}} an element's text/alt text to the clipboard.
{{c1::;y}} - {{c2::copy}} an element's link URL to the clipboard.
{{c1::;#}} - {{c2::copy}} an element's anchor URL to the clipboard.
